doctype html
html
  head
    meta(http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Nova Amostra Disponível para Análise

    style.
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
  body(style="font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f7fa; margin: 0; padding: 0;")
    table(role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%")
      tr
        td(align="center" style="padding: 40px 20px;")
          div(style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: linear-gradient(to right, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); position: relative;")
            
            div(style="position: relative; z-index: 10; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px; margin: 20px;")
              div(style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 24px;")
                div(style="text-align: center; color: white;")
                 h1(style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;")
                  span(style="display: inline-block; width: 24px; height: 24px; vertical-align: middle;")
                    svg(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: #FFD700; width: 24px; height: 24px;")
                      path(d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z")
                      line(x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13")
                      line(x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17")

                  h2(style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 24px;") Uma nova amostra foi disponibilizada para análise na plataforma SuperDot.

                  div(style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: left;")
                    ul(style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;")
                      li(style="margin-bottom: 6px;")
                        b Amostra:
                        |  #{sample}
                      li(style="margin-bottom: 6px;")
                        b Pesquisa:
                        |  #{sampleName}
                      li(style="margin-bottom: 6px;")
                        b Status da amostra:
                        |  #{sampleStatus}
                      li(style="margin-bottom: 6px;")
                        b Instituição:
                        |  #{sampleInstituition}
                      li(style="margin-bottom: 6px;")
                        b Data de envio:
                        |  #{submissionDate}
                      if senderName
                        li(style="margin-bottom: 6px;")
                          b Enviada por:
                          |  #{senderName} (#{senderEmail})
                      if sampleDescription
                        li(style="margin-bottom: 6px;")
                          b Descrição:
                          span(style="display: block; margin-top: 4px; font-style: italic; opacity: 0.9;") "#{sampleDescription}"

                  a(href=systemURL target="_blank" style="display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.3s ease; margin-bottom: 24px;") Analisar Amostra

                  p(style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);") Caso o botão não funcione, copie e cole esta URL no navegador:
                  p(style="word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);") #{systemURL}

            div(style="position: relative; z-index: 10; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); font-size: 12px;")
              p(style="margin: 0;") Essa mensagem é automática e não deve ser respondida.

    style.
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        div[style*="padding: 40px"] {
          padding: 20px !important;
        }

        div[style*="width: 200px"] {
          width: 150px !important;
          height: 150px !important;
        }
      }
      a:hover {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3) !important;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) !important;
        transform: translateY(-2px) !important;
      }